description:
First on today’s episode, Nina Dobrev, Anna, and Sim chat with…

…Caden in Utah who loves his wife of six months…but doesn’t love how he’s been losing friends since they got married and doesn’t know whether he should focus on his marriage or on his friendships.

Then, we crack into the Unqualified caller vault to revisit a call from Jaime Pressly’s episode…

…Breanne is 33 years old, newly single, and ready to mingle after recently moving to London! But she’s noticing that all the men she’s been dating seem to be scared off by her age and is looking for some age-positive dating advice!

Don’t forget to visit unqualified.com/contact to share your feedback and relationship questions – we love hearing from you!
